I '''Johann Ernst Elias Bessler''' (1680 - Nobiembri 30, 1745) metung yang entrepreneur nung nu pepakit na deng tukituking gamit a papakit da ing ausan dang [[alang anggang kimut (perpetual motion)]].

== Bie at Carera ==
I Bessler mibait ya king balen a [[Zittau]] king [[Saxony]], [[Germany]] inyang 1680. Inyang 1712 linto ya king balen ning [[Gera]] king [[lalawigan ning Reuss]] at pepalto ne ing "pangsariling "gagalong parugang" (self-moving wheel), nung nu mga {{convert|6.5|ft|m}} keng sukad bilug(diameter) ampong {{convert|4|in|cm}} kakapal. MIsan atiu keng gagalong kabilian atin yang upayang abuat ing mapilan a bayat (pounds).{{Fact|date=October 2007}}

